OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with bright or occasional
OL,6,Fsunny spells throughout the day. Cloud
OL,7,Fincreasing to bring some outbreaks of
OL,8,Flight showery rain by the early
OL,9,Fevening. Feeling warm in sunshine.
OL,10,FBreezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy at first with breaks
OL,13,Fdeveloping in the west and spreading
OL,14,Feastwards as the rain clears, giving a
OL,15,Fdry and settled evening with easing
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
