OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FLargely dry and cloudy with
OL,6,Fsome isolated light showers at first
OL,7,Fthen sunny spells developing during
OL,8,Fthe afternoon with light and variable
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FLargely
OL,12,Fdry with bright or sunny spells on
OL,13,FSunday. Cloudier on Monday and Tuesday
OL,14,Fwith showers spreading inland from
OL,15,Fcoastal areas. Feeling cooler,
OL,16,Fespecially along windward coastal
OL,17,Fdistricts.
